          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For you, O Lord, are supreme over all the earth; you are exalted far above all gods. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For you, O Lord, are supreme over all the earth; you are exalted far above all gods."
